<span class="person">Lucy Whalley</span> is a PhD student at Imperial 
College London. She uses high performance computing, Python and quantum 
mechanics to model photovoltaic materials. She is a qualified 
mathematics teacher, and believes that the best way to understand 
something is to teach it.  </p>
